column5: Durable folding knife with compact flip design: Quick-flip folding design combines a compact size with pro-grade durability—ideal for tradespeople who need a reliable, portable knife that fits easily in your pocket or belt., Built-in blade storage and ABS handle: Integrated storage holds 3 blades inside the handle, with an ABS grip for added control, comfort, and reduced hand fatigue during repetitive cutting., Includes 10 SK5 blackened utility blades Made from hardened SK5 steel for superior edge retention, these blades are optimized to deliver sharp, accurate cuts and resist snapping under pressure., Quick and safe blade changes: Change blades in seconds using the tool-free release button. Stay productive on the job without wasting time or handling blades unsafely., Safe blade dispenser and full compatibility Blade pack includes a dispenser for safe blade handling. Blades fit all OX utility knives and most standard-size box cutters and folding knives on the market.
column54:
The OX PRO Utility Folding Knife + 10PK Blade Combo is a high-performance folding box cutter knife combo designed for pros. The utility knife features a foldable compact design with one-touch blade change, a built-in wire cutter and stripper, and a durable metal body with a secure ABS plastic grip for added comfort. 

The integrated blade storage compartment holds up to 3 extra blades—so you’re always ready when a blade wears down. Also included is a 10-pack of premium blackened SK5 steel blades, designed for strength, edge retention and durability. 

These blades are hardened and tempered to resist chipping, bending and breakage. Whether you're slicing through drywall, insulation, plastic, or packaging, this combo ensures you have plenty of backup blades to keep going. 

Each blade is double-sided and compatible with all standard-size utility knives, and comes in a dispenser for safe storage. Suitable for contractors, electricians, and tradespeople seeking a compact folding utility knife.
column55: The OX PRO Folding Knife + 10PK SK5 Blades Combo is built for serious pros. Featuring a compact flip design box cutter, tool-free blade change, built-in wire cutter, and integrated blade storage, it’s perfect for all construction professionals. Includes 10 ultra-tough SK5 blackened blades in a dispenser. Suitable for electricians, contractors, and tradespeople who demand reliable tools that last.

column54: Built with the tradesman in mind, the OX Trade 4 Piece Level Set is go-to toolset for trade professionals who demand durable accuracy on every job. This set includes four essential levels: the 600mm, 1200mm, and 1800mm Trade Levels, along with a 230mm Torpedo Level—covering all the bases for large and small leveling tasks alike. Crafted from high-quality, lightweight aluminium, each level offers robust construction that stands up to the wear and tear of everyday use in tough job site conditions. The UV-resistant vials ensure reliable performance, even under harsh sunlight, and the solid acrylic vials provide an exceptional accuracy of 0.5mm (0.0005in/in), so you can trust the measurements in every application. The 230mm Torpedo Level, equipped with a magnetic V-groove, is perfect for working on pipes, scaffolding, or any other hard-to-reach areas, adding extra functionality to your toolkit. The OX Trade 4 Piece Level Set is backed by OX’s commitment to quality, featuring a lifetime vial warranty that guarantees long-lasting performance and accuracy.
column55: The OX Trade 4 Piece Level Set is a durable yet lightweight aluminium set that includes 600mm, 1200mm, and 1800mm Trade Levels, plus a 230mm Torpedo Level. Featuring UV-resistant, solid acrylic vials with 0.5mm (0.0005in/in) accuracy, these levels are built to withstand harsh conditions. The magnetic V-groove on the Torpedo Level makes it ideal for pipe and scaffold work. Backed by a lifetime vial warranty, this set is built to last.

column55:
Built with the tradesman in mind, the OX Pro Series Tuff Levels are designed to take a beating. The aluminum
body of the level is one solid piece, without handles or room for cement, mud, and other debris to get clogged.
The level includes three vials, one for level, two for plumb. The vials consistently provide an accuracy of 0. 005"/
1" or . 5mm/ m and are protected by structural reinforcement within the level. On each end of the body there
are rubber end caps to protect the level from bumps, drops, and excess damage. The top and bottom of the level
are both milled surfaces giving it a perfectly at edge and ensuring increased accuracy compared to a coated
surface.

Its superior cutting ability allows for smooth, clean cuts through asphalt, reducing downtime and increasing productivity. The blade's design also minimizes vibrations, resulting in greater operator comfort and precision.

column54: Built with the tradesman in mind, the OX Ultrastrike Framing Hammer is comfortable yet powerful. The OX Ultrastrike Framing Hammers are constructed from one-piece of forged steel which is built to withstand any jobsite condition. The magnetic nail starter on the head allows for simple handling and overall use as it is easier for you to line up your nail precisely. The bridged neck of the hammer is designed to absorb strike shock and vibration which reduces user strain. Limiting the vibration of the hammer helps to reduce repetitive stress injuries and pains. Built tough and durable, the hammer is also designed to be comfortable and ergonomic for day-to-day use. The nonslip OX Grip is made to help users hold the hammer with ease while remaining comfortable throughout the working day. The hammer is heat treated to give it greater overall durability as well as allow it to last longer over time.
column55: OX Tools Ultrastrike Framing Hammers are created with the tradesmen in mind. This Ultrastrike Framing Hammer was designed by professionals, for professionals. Our non-slip OX Grip handle and bridged neck for shock reduction help you to live the trade. Forged, one piece steel construction ensures the durability of the tool while the magnetic nail starter allows for easier handling and use.

column54:
The OX Pro 3lbs Club Hammer combines durability, precision, and comfort to deliver reliable performance in demanding tasks. Featuring a forged steel head, this hammer provides exceptional strength and impact resistance, making it ideal for breaking masonry, driving chisels, and splitting wood. The 3-pound head ensures substantial striking force, while its compact design offers maximum control and maneuverability, making it a versatile choice for both heavy-duty and precision work.

The hammer is equipped with a genuine American straight hickory handle, renowned for its strength, flexibility, and ability to absorb shocks from heavy strikes. This handle ensures stability during high-impact tasks and enhances user control. To further elevate comfort and usability, the handle is fitted with a non-slip TPR grip, providing a secure hold and reducing hand fatigue, even during prolonged use or in wet conditions.

The head is securely affixed to the handle to prevent detachment during heavy-duty applications. Additionally, overstrike protection reinforces the handle against damage caused by missed strikes, ensuring a longer tool life and improved durability.
column55: The OX Tools 3lbs Club Hammer combines power, precision, and durability for demanding tasks. Featuring a forged steel head, a genuine American straight hickory handle, and a non-slip TPR grip, this hammer delivers strong impacts, superior control, and reduced vibration. With safety features like overstrike protection and a securely attached head, it’s ideal for masonry, demolition, and more.
column56: Heavy-Duty Forged Steel Head: The 3lb forged steel head delivers substantial striking power, perfect for breaking concrete, driving chisels, or splitting wood., Straight Hickory Handle: Genuine American straight hickory provides exceptional durability, shock absorption, and resistance to splintering for enhanced performance., Ergonomic TPR Non-Slip Grip: The ergonomic TPR grip ensures a secure hold and reduces hand fatigue, offering comfort and precision even during prolonged use., Overstrike Protection: Reinforced design protects the handle from damage caused by missed strikes, extending the tool's lifespan and ensuring consistent reliability., Secure Head Attachment: Engineered for safety, the head is securely affixed to the handle, eliminating the risk of detachment during heavy-duty tasks., Versatile Application: Suitable for masonry work, demolition, driving stakes, and splitting rocks, this hammer is a reliable tool for professionals and DIY enthusiasts alike., Heat-Treated Construction: The heat-treated steel head ensures long-lasting durability and exceptional resistance to wear, even in the toughest job site conditions.

column5: Forged One-Piece Steel Head: Ensures unmatched durability and strength of the OX, delivering reliable performance in even the toughest jobsite conditions., Smooth Face Design: Reduces surface damage on materials, making it perfect for framing and precision carpentry work where a clean finish is essential., American Hickory Handle: Crafted from premium hickory wood for reduced vibration, providing secure striking, comfort and minimizing strain during extended hammering., Laser-Etched Grip: The ergonomically designed handle offers a secure hold, easy identification and enhanced comfort, ensuring precision and control for every swing., Magnetic Nail Starter: Allows for quick and accurate nail placement, improving efficiency and safety, especially when working at height or with one hand., Straight Handle Contour: Designed to fit the natural shape of a contractor’s hand, providing better control, comfort, and reduced fatigue., Professional-Grade Durability: Built with high-quality materials to withstand daily use in framing, carpentry, and general construction, ensuring a long service life.
column54:
The OX Pro 16-Ounce Smooth Face Framing Hammer features a forged one-piece steel head, this hammer delivers unmatched strength and durability for consistent performance in framing, carpentry, and construction tasks. Its smooth face minimizes surface damage on materials, making it ideal for precision work.

The American hickory handle not only provides exceptional durability but also significantly reduces vibration, minimizing fatigue and the risk of strain during extended use. The handle's laser-etched grip offers enhanced ergonomics, ensuring a secure and comfortable hold, even in challenging conditions. column2: OX Dual Thrust Caulking Gun – 400ml
column3: General Hand Tools > Caulk & Sausage Guns > Caulk Guns
column5: Patented toggle switch to easily change thrust & stroke. Switchable ratio (12:1 / 24:1) function to enable easy application of all viscosity adhesives and sealants., Patented 360° Steel riveted rotating carriage, Twin heat-treated steel push plates for greater strength, Impact‐resistant Nylon/Fiberglass handle & trigger with TPE rubber overmold, Smooth thrust action
column54:
The OX Dual Thrust Caulking Gun – 400ml, a pinnacle of innovation and craftsmanship in the world of sealant application. Engineered with precision and designed for professionals, this caulking gun boasts revolutionary features that redefine efficiency and ease of use.
At its core lies our patented toggle switch, offering unparalleled control over thrust and stroke, coupled with the groundbreaking 360° Steel riveted rotating carriage for seamless maneuverability in any application scenario. Versatility is key, thanks to its switchable ratio (12:1 / 24:1) function, ensuring effortless dispensing of adhesives and sealants of varying viscosities.
Durability meets performance with twin heat-treated steel push plates, providing unmatched strength and reliability even under the most demanding conditions. The ergonomic design is not just about comfort but about resilience, with a nylon and fiberglass handle trigger featuring TPE rubber over mold for impact resistance, ensuring prolonged use without fatigue.
Experience fluidity in operation with smooth thrust action, while the rigid polymer handle guarantees both strength and longevity. Equipped with a robust 1.5mm steel push piston, this caulking gun effortlessly accommodates up to 400ml cartridges, catering to a wide range of project needs with ease and precision.#
But the innovation doesn't stop there. A thoughtful addition of a steel pin on the underside allows for convenient puncturing of dried caulk, ensuring uninterrupted workflow and hassle-free maintenance. Dominate your sealant applications with confidence and precision, backed by the reliability of OX Pro craftsmanship.
column55: The OX Pro Dual Thrust Sealant Gun features cutting edge technology like our patented toggle switch to easily change thrust and stroke and our patented 360° Steel riveted rotating carriage. Its switchable ratio (12:1 / 24:1) function enables easy application of all viscosity adhesives and sealants. Twin heat-treated steel push plates offer greater strength and its nylon and fibreglass handle trigger with TPE rubber over mold are both impact-resistant. It features smooth thrust action, a rigid polymer handle for strength and durability and a 1.5mm steel push piston for dispensing up to 400ml cartridges. A steel pin on underside allows you to puncture dried caulk.

The OX Pro 3-Inch Oil Tanned Leather Tool Belt - Large 35" to 46". Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, this belt is engineered for unparalleled durability and all-day comfort, catering to the needs of professional tradespeople. Constructed from premium top grain oil tanned saddle leather, it embodies superior quality and longevity, ensuring it withstands the rigors of daily use on job sites.
Designed with convenience in mind, this tool belt offers effortless access to all essential tools and hardware, enhancing efficiency and productivity. Its perimeter stitching reinforcement enhances tear resistance, guaranteeing resilience against the toughest challenges encountered on-site. The inclusion of a sturdy double-notch steel clasp, heavy-duty rivet reinforcement, and antique bronze finish hardware underscores its robust construction and timeless aesthetic appeal.
Versatility is paramount, as the Pro Tool Belt seamlessly integrates with OX Pro leather tool pouches, optimizing organization and accessibility. Suitable for waist sizes ranging from 35" to 46", it can be easily adjusted to accommodate various body types and preferences. The 3-inch width provides optimal support without sacrificing mobility, while the ergonomic design ensures a comfortable fit throughout extended work periods
column55: Built for all-day comfort, OX Pro Oil Tanned Leather 3 in Belt provides professional tradespeople easy access to all their tools and hardware on-site. Made from high-quality top grain oil tanned saddle leather, this professional tool belt comes with perimeter stitching reinforcement to increase tear resistance and make it tough enough to take on whatever the job site throws at you. It comes with a sturdy double notch steel clasp, heavy duty rivet reinforcement and antique, bronze finish hardware. Perfect for us with the OX Pro leather tool pouches. Suitable for waist sizes 29” - 46” and can be adjusted to  3” / 76mm wide.

column54:
The Ultimate Shark Diamond Blade - Asphalt - 450/25.4mm, a game-changer in asphalt cutting technology. Designed meticulously to cater to the demands of professionals, this blade stands out with its unparalleled efficiency and precision. Crafted with a 10mm segment height, it effortlessly slices through asphalt with ease, ensuring swift and smooth operations.
What sets this blade apart is its ingenious design features. The incorporation of a wedge segment enhances cutting speed and accuracy, minimizing the time and effort required for each task. Furthermore, the addition of undercut protection guarantees durability, safeguarding the blade against wear and tear even in the harshest conditions.
The U clearance gullet is another standout feature, facilitating efficient debris removal during cutting, thereby reducing friction and heat buildup. This not only prolongs the blade's lifespan but also ensures consistent performance throughout its usage.
Professionals across various industries, from construction to road maintenance, will appreciate the reliability and versatility of the Ultimate Shark Diamond Blade. Whether you're working on highways, parking lots, or driveways, this blade delivers consistent results, making it an indispensable tool in your arsenal. 
Experience the pinnacle of cutting excellence with the Ultimate Shark Diamond Blade - Asphalt - 450/25.4mm
column55: The Ultimate Shark Diamond Blade - Asphalt - 450/25.4mm is an asphalt blade with a 10mm segment height. Its clever design includes a wedge segment, undercut protection and a U clearance gullet.

Part of the Spectrum Superior range of diamond blades, this 300mm/12" blade delivers speed, durability, and versatility. Designed with a reinforced centre plate for added safety and precision, this blade features turbo segments for aggressive, high-speed cutting. Integrated cooling holes help reduce heat build-up during extended use, maintaining blade stability and extending its life—even under intense site conditions. From construction sites to demolition jobs, this blade is guaranteed to cut all construction materials, including ferrous and non-ferrous metals. It's ideal for use with 12" disc cutters and angle grinders that accept a 20mm bore and operate up to 6400 RPM. Whether you’re facing a tough mix of building materials or need a reliable go-to blade for varied site work, the Spectrum Pro Turbo Multi-Steel blade is your ultimate cutting solution. Trusted by professionals for its cutting speed, durability, and all-material performance.

column2: OX Pro Utility Folding Knife - w/ Blades
column3: General Hand Tools > Cutting > Knives & Blades
column5: Quick-flip folding action for fast access: Opens and closes smoothly with one hand thanks to the quick-flip mechanism, allowing compact storage and safe use—ideal for trades needing instant access to their cutter., Blade storage compartment: Stores up to 3 spare blades securely inside the handle, so you're never caught without a sharp replacement—ideal for high-volume users working through tough materials., Durable build with ABS grip and metal body: Designed to handle tough site conditions, the aluminum body ensures strength while the ABS plastic grip improves comfort and control during long periods of cutting or stripping., Tool-free blade change system: The easy-release button allows users to change blades quickly and safely without tools, keeping workflow smooth and reducing the time spent on maintenance in fast-paced environments., Built-in wire cutter and stripper: An integrated wire cutter and stripper add everyday utility for electricians and other pros dealing with cabling—reducing the need to switch tools and boosting on-site efficiency., Clip and tether-ready: Belt clip and lanyard hole offer two secure carry options for on-person access or tool tethering, keeping your knife close and secure whether you're climbing ladders or working overhead.
column54:
The OX Pro Utility Folding Knife with Blade Storage is a high-performance folding box cutter knife designed for pros. Featuring a rugged metal body and enhanced with an ABS plastic grip, this knife combines strength with ergonomic comfort, ideal for repetitive cutting tasks across a wide range of applications.

Designed for speed, the Pro Folding Utility Knife features a quick-flip mechanism that allows for rapid one-handed opening and folding, making it perfect for tight spots and time-critical jobs. The quick blade release button ensures fast and safe blade changes with no tools required - just press and switch. It comes preloaded with three SK5 blackened blades in the integrated blade storage, so you always have replacements on hand when you need them most.

For added versatility, this folding utility knife also includes a built-in wire stripper and cutter, making it a go-to choice for electricians, data installers, HVAC and general contractors alike. The slim, compact design is easy to carry, and a belt clip and lanyard hole provide flexible storage options to keep the knife secure and accessible at all times.

Compatible with all standard utility knife blades, the OX PRO Utility Folding Knife is a compact powerhouse built to deliver consistent, reliable cutting performance.

Includes 3x SK5 blackened blades and accepts all standard utility blades.

column54: Built with the tradesman in mind, the OX Tools Pro 20oz Ultrastrike Brick Hammer is comfortable yet powerful. The brick hammer includes a one-piece forged steel head which is built to withstand any jobsite condition. The bridged neck of the hammer is designed to absorb strike shock and vibration which reduces user strain. Limiting the vibration of the hammer helps to reduce repetitive stress injuries and pains. Built tough and durable, the hammer is also designed to be comfortable and ergonomic for day-to-day use. The non-slip OX Grip is made to help users hold the hammer with ease while remaining comfortable throughout the working day. The hammer is heat treated to give it greater overall durability as well as allow it to last longer over time.
column55: The OX Tools Pro Ultrastrike Brick Hammer is built with the tradesmen in mind. The brick hammer head is constructed from forged steel for extreme durability. column5: STRONG STRIKING - Gapped bridge neck leaves more weight at the head of the hammer, giving it a stronger striking force for its weight., CONVENIENT - Magnetic nail starter allows for easier handling and use., BRIDGED NECK - Dissipates vibration and strike shock which reduces user strain., ERGONOMIC - Non-slip OX Grip designed to help users hold hammer with ease while remaining comfortable during all day use., DURABLE - The body of the hammer is entirely steel with an outer coating to ensure ultimate durability and reduce the risk of deterioration.
column54: Built with the tradesman in mind, the OX Ultrastrike Framing Hammer is comfortable yet powerful. The OX Ultrastrike Framing Hammers are constructed from one-piece of forged steel which is built to withstand any jobsite condition. The magnetic nail starter on the head allows for simple handling and overall use as it is easier for you to line up your nail precisely. The bridged neck of the hammer is designed to absorb strike shock and vibration which reduces user strain. Limiting the vibration of the hammer helps to reduce repetitive stress injuries and pains. Built tough and durable, the hammer is also designed to be comfortable and ergonomic for day-to-day use. The nonslip OX Grip is made to help users hold the hammer with ease while remaining comfortable throughout the working day. The hammer is heat treated to give it greater overall durability as well as allow it to last longer over time.
column55: OX Tools Ultrastrike Framing Hammers are created with the tradesmen in mind. This Ultrastrike Framing Hammer was designed by professionals, for professionals. Our non-slip OX Grip handle and bridged neck for shock reduction help you to live the trade. Forged, one piece steel construction ensures the durability of the tool while the magnetic nail starter allows for easier handling and use.

column5: Ergonomic Etched Handle: Slight angled knife profile and textured handle grip to reduce fatigue and improve control during extended or repetitive use., Durable Metal Body: Rugged metal housing built to endure daily site use, drops, and tough materials, for reliable performance and durability, day in and out., Tool-Free Quick Blade Change: Quick-release button allows fast, safe blade swaps without tools—keeping workflow efficient and reducing downtime on site., 5x SK5 Double-Sided Blades Included: Preloaded with 5 ultra-sharp SK5 utility blades, each double-sided for extended life and fewer box cutter blade changes., Internal Blade Storage & Lanyard Hole: Store up to 5 replacement utility blades inside. Tether hole keeps your knife secure and always within reach on the job.
column54:
The OX Pro Retractable Utility Knife is a professional-grade box cutter built for serious construction tasks. Featuring a heavy-duty metal body and a slightly angled ergonomic handle, it offers superior handle grip and superior comfort, ideal for repetitive tasks.

Equipped with 5 SK5 blackened double-sided blades, and internal blade storage holds up to 5 replacements, so you're always prepared without needing to return to your toolbox. The quick-release blade change button makes swapping blades fast, tool-free, and safe, perfect for fast-paced job sites where efficiency matters.

This pro retractable utility knife is compatible all standard-size utility blades for universal compatibility and job site convenience. The built-in tether/lanyard hole offers easy access and storage on the tool belt or wall hooks. 

Whether you're opening boxes, cutting insulation, or trimming materials, the OX Pro Retractable Utility Knife offers rugged reliability, comfort, control and pro-level performance.

column2: Pro 22-Ounce Milled Face Framing Hammer | Straight Hickory Handle w/ TPR Grip
column3: General Hand Tools > Striking & Demolition > Framing Hammers
column5: Forged One-Piece Steel Head: Engineered for extreme durability, the robust steel head ensures long-lasting performance and reliable strength on tough job sites., Milled Face Design: The textured surface provides a better grip on nail heads, minimizing glancing blows and maximizing precision for efficient nailing., Genuine American Hickory Handle: Reduces vibration and absorbs shocks, offering enhanced control and minimizing fatigue for safer, more comfortable use., Ergonomic TPR Rubber Grip: The contoured grip provides superior comfort, control, and shock absorption, ensuring reduced hand strain during extended use., Magnetic Nail Starter: Simplifies one-handed nail placement, enhancing convenience and accuracy for faster and more efficient work on framing and construction tasks., Straight Claw Design: Offers superior leverage for extracting embedded nails, facilitates removal in tight spaces, and minimizes damage to surrounding wood surfaces., Versatile Performance: Perfect for framing, woodworking, carpentry, and construction, this hammer delivers ultimate striking power and precision for a variety of tasks.
column54:
The OX Tools Pro 22 oz Framing Hammer is the perfect combination of power, durability, and comfort, making it a must-have tool for professional tradesmen and DIY enthusiasts alike. Designed to excel in framing, finishing, woodworking, and construction tasks, this California-style framing hammer boasts a robust construction and thoughtful design to deliver superior performance and reduced user fatigue.

At the heart of the hammer lies its forged one-piece steel head, engineered to withstand the toughest job site conditions. The milled face ensures precision and prevents glancing blows, making it ideal for driving nails efficiently and accurately. Whether you’re building frames or finishing woodwork, the textured surface of the hammer head provides an enhanced grip on nail heads, ensuring consistency and reliability.

The handle of this hammer is crafted from genuine American hickory, a material renowned for its strength, durability, and natural shock-absorbing properties. This reduces vibration and minimizes the risk of injury, even during extended use. column3: General Hand Tools > Caulk & Sausage Guns > Caulk Guns
column5: Dual Thrust Ratios (25:1 / 12:1) – Switch between high and low thrust ratios for versatility in applying both high-viscosity and lighter caulks, ensuring optimal performance with any material., Dripless On/Off Switch for Clean Application – Instantly stop caulk flow with the dripless switch, reducing material waste and keeping your job site clean for professional results every time., Built-In Spout Cutter for Quick Prep – The integrated spout cutter allows for easy and safe opening of caulk tubes, eliminating the need for additional tools., Seal Punch for Easy Tube Puncturing – Built-in seal punch breaks the inner seal of caulk tubes, speeding up setup and eliminating the need for extra tools., Durable Steel, Aluminum, and PP Construction – Built with tough, long-lasting materials to withstand heavy use on demanding job sites, ensuring a reliable performance over time., Ergonomic Handle for Comfortable Use – Designed for extended use, the ergonomic handle reduces hand fatigue while providing a firm, comfortable grip for better control., Ideal for Various Sealing Applications – Perfect for both professional and DIY jobs, ideal for sealing windows, doors, trim, and construction joints with high or low-viscosity sealants.
column54: The OX Pro 400mL Heavy-Duty Caulk Gun with dual thrust ratios (25:1 / 12:1) is designed to provide versatility, precision, and power for all your sealing needs. The 25:1 thrust ratio is ideal for high-viscosity sealants and adhesives, offering optimal force for controlled, smooth application, while the 12:1 thrust ratio is perfect for lighter caulks, offering greater ease of use for less demanding materials. This allows you to switch between the two settings for different tasks without the need for multiple tools. Featuring a dripless on/off switch, the caulk gun allows you to stop the flow of caulk instantly, reducing waste and keeping your work area clean. Whether you’re sealing large surfaces or finishing up detailed jobs, the ability to control the flow of material ensures professional results with minimal mess. The built-in spout cutter makes opening new sealant tubes quick and easy, while the seal punch eliminates the need for additional tools to break the inner seal, helping you start your job quickly. Constructed from a robust combination of steel, aluminum, and PP, this caulk gun is built to withstand demanding job sites, ensuring durability and long-term reliability.
column55: The OX Pro 400mL Heavy-Duty Caulk Gun features dual thrust ratios (25:1 / 12:1) for precision across a range of materials, with a dripless on/off switch for clean, controlled application. A built-in spout cutter and seal punch ensure quick setup, while the steel, aluminum, and PP construction provides durability for tough job sites. Ideal for both high- and low-viscosity caulks, it delivers consistent results with minimal waste.

column2: Pro Tuff Level 24" / 600mm
column3: General Hand Tools > Layout > Levels
column5: Ultimate strength for durability on the job site, Lightweight aluminium profile for reduced strain when using for long durations or at difficult angles, Uncluttered profile reduces the amount of cement/ mud and debris that could clog and ensures easy cleaning, Ultra-precise level vials calibrated to 0.005”/” (0.5mm/m), Ribbed profile for easy pickup
column55:
Built with the tradesman in mind, the OX Pro Series Tuff Levels are designed to take a beating. The aluminum
body of the level is one solid piece, without handles or room for cement, mud, and other debris to get clogged.
The level includes three vials, one for level, two for plumb. The vials consistently provide an accuracy of 0. 005"/
1" or . 5mm/ m and are protected by structural reinforcement within the level. On each end of the body there
are rubber end caps to protect the level from bumps, drops, and excess damage. The top and bottom of the level
are both milled surfaces giving it a perfectly at edge and ensuring increased accuracy compared to a coated
surface.

The skeleton frame design keeps this caulking gun lightweight while maintaining the strength needed for tough job site conditions. One of its standout features is the drip-to-non-drip switch, allowing seamless transition between continuous flow and controlled release to prevent excess caulk waste. The integrated spout cutter makes tube preparation effortless, while the seal punch quickly pierces the inner foil seal—eliminating the need for extra tools. Designed for comfort and ease of use, this caulk gun features an ergonomic trigger that reduces hand fatigue, even during extended sealing tasks. Its steel and aluminum construction ensures long-lasting durability, while the compact skeleton frame allows for better visibility and control in tight spaces. Whether sealing windows, doors, trim, or joints, the OX Pro Skeleton Caulk Gun is your go-to tool for precision and reliability.

With 13 snap-off segments per blade, you'll always have a fresh edge ready to go, making these blades ideal for repetitive, high-precision cutting tasks across drywall, packaging, flooring, vinyl, insulation, and more.

Whether you're trimming delicate materials or tackling tougher substrates, the sharpness and stability of these blades help reduce fatigue and improve accuracy.

column2: Pro Heavy-Duty Fixed Blade Folding Knife | Includes 3 Blades
column3: General Hand Tools > Cutting > Knives & Blades
column5: Zinc Alloy Upper Body and High Grade Aluminum Handle, Quick Folding action for quick cutting and storage., Notched thumb rest increases grip., Notched blade holder makes for easy work, Ergonomic handle design for all day comfort., Strong lightweight construction, Ergonomically designed handle
column54: Built with the tradesman in mind, the OX Pro Heavy-Duty Fixed Blade Folding Knife is the toughest folding utility knife in the pro series. Built from a high-grade zinc alloy upper body and an aluminium alloy handle, it strikes the perfect balance between strength and lightweight handling. Whether you're cutting drywall, slicing insulation, stripping wire, or opening boxes, this knife delivers consistent performance and job site ready reliability. A standout feature is its tool-less blade change system. The rear compartment enables fast blade swaps with a simple push-button release. No downtime, no hassle. With a quick-fold action, the knife opens swiftly and locks securely, making it easy to deploy and stow away between cuts. A notched thumb rest enhances grip and control, letting you apply more pressure with confidence. The underside of the blade holder includes built-in notches designed for wire stripping and strap cutting — adding even more versatility. Ergonomically shaped for comfort during all-day use, this knife is made to feel solid in the hand without weighing you down. Supplied with three utility blades, it’s ready to go straight out of the box. The OX Pro Folding Knife: compact, capable, and built for the trade.
column55: The OX Pro Heavy Duty Fixed Blade Folding Knife offers quick fold action, ultra-sharp steel blades and a strong, lightweight construction that makes cutting materials easy. column5: Flip-open folding design: The quick flip mechanism allows for fast one-handed opening and safe folding when not in use, offering compact storage and quick access for professionals on the move., Durable metal body with etched grip: Built for jobsite durability, the metal construction and textured handle provide a secure grip and enhanced control—especially useful in tight or awkward cutting angles., Tool-free blade change: A simple release button enables fast, safe blade changes without the need for tools—keeping you efficient on the job and reducing downtime during repetitive tasks., Belt clip and tether hole: Multiple storage options include a rear belt clip for easy access and a tether hole for secure attachment—ensuring the knife is always within reach and never misplaced., Integrated wire cutter and stripper: Designed with electricians in mind, the built-in wire cutter and stripper add extra versatility to your tool belt—ideal for electrical tasks and light cabling work., Standard blade compatibility: Compatible with all standard-size utility blades, the knife includes one premium SK5 blackened blade with ultra-sharp cutting edges ready for use straight out of the box.
column54:
The OX Pro Utility Knife is a pro-grade box cutter for professionals that prefer the compact convenience of a folding knife. Built with a durable metal body and etched grip handle, this folding utility knife fits comfortably in your pocket while packing all the performance you need on site.

With a quick blade change release button, swapping blades is safe and hassle-free, no tools needed. It comes preloaded with 1x SK5 blackened blade and is compatible with standard-size utility blades.

Designed for speed, strength, and portability, this compact folding knife allows for quick flip opening and closing. For added utility, it includes an integrated wire cutter and stripper, making it a top pick for electricians and multi-trade contractors.

A slim profile, belt clip, and tether/lanyard hole make this knife ultra-convenient for everyday job site use.

Engineered for durability and control in every cut, the OX Pro Folding Utility Knife is a top-selling choice for trade professionals, ready whenever and wherever the job takes you.

column5: Easy read laser etched markings, Reinforced locking nut for secure transfer of angles, High-quality stainless-steel blade with double-sided scale, UV ABS glass-filled nylon handle, Built in dual vials offering extra functionality and accuracy
column54:
Introducing the OX Trade Sliding Bevel - 200mm, a precision tool engineered for professionals who demand accuracy and durability. This bevel is meticulously crafted with a double-sided scale, allowing for exact replication and transfer of angles, ensuring your projects meet the highest standards of precision. The reinforced locking nut guarantees that once set, the angle remains securely in place, eliminating the risk of slippage and ensuring consistent results.
The OX Trade Sliding Bevel is equipped with built-in dual vials, adding a layer of functionality that makes it indispensable for any job site. Whether you are working on intricate carpentry, detailed joinery, or precise metalworking, these vials help you achieve perfectly level and plumb angles every time.
The handle of the bevel is manufactured from UV-stabilized ABS glass-filled nylon, providing exceptional strength and durability. This robust material ensures that the handle can withstand the rigors of daily use, resisting wear and tear, and maintaining its structural integrity even under the most demanding conditions.
Designed with the professional in mind, the OX Trade Sliding Bevel - 200mm is not only a tool but a reliable partner in your craftsmanship. Its ergonomic design offers a comfortable grip, making it easy to use for extended periods without fatigue. This bevel is perfect for a wide range of applications, from laying out complex joinery angles to ensuring accurate cuts in metalwork, making it an essential addition to any professional’s toolkit.
Invest in the OX Trade Sliding Bevel - 200mm and experience the confidence that comes with using a tool designed for precision, reliability, and durability. Whether you’re in construction, carpentry, or metalworking, this bevel will enhance your efficiency and accuracy, helping you to achieve perfect results every time
column55: The OX Trade Sliding Bevel 200mm is specially designed with a double sided scale and reinforced locking nut to ensure unparalleled precision and reliability when replicating and transferring angles. With a built in dual vias offering additional functionality, the bevel handle is manufactured from a UV ABS glass-filled nylon handle, designed to withstand the demands and challenges of daily use.
column56: Easy read laser etched markings, Reinforced locking nut for secure transfer of angles, High-quality stainless-steel blade with double-sided scale, UV ABS glass-filled nylon handle, Built in dual vials offering extra functionality and accuracy

surface.

column5: 8-Point SK5 Snap-Off Blade: Includes a premium SK5 18mm blackened blade with 8 snap-off points, giving you fresh, razor-sharp edges for consistent precision across light-duty cutting tasks., Durable ABS Body: Constructed from high-quality ABS plastic for strength without the weight, easy to handle and perfect for reducing fatigue during repetitive, minor cutting tasks., Slide Lock Cutting Depth Control: Multi-position slide lock lets you quickly adjust and lock the blade to your desired cutting depth, keeping the boxcutter steady and safe while you work., Removable End Cap Blade Snapper: Built-in snapper on the end cap makes it fast and safe to break off used blade segments, giving you a sharp tip instantly without extra tools or effort., Universal 18mm Snap-off Blade Compatibility: Designed for easy blade replacement and compatible with standard 18mm snap-off blades, so you can keep cutting without slowing down the task at hand.
column54: The OX Trade 18mm Snap-Off Utility Knife is a compact retractable boxcutter made for everyday cutting tasks. Designed for convenience, this utility knife features a SK5 18mm/0.7″ blackened blade with 8 snap-off points. When the blade dulls, just break it off for a new sharp blade edge. The removable end cap doubles as a blade snapper for a safer and faster renewal of the worn-out blade edge. When it’s time to replace the entire boxcutter blade, the quick-change mechanism makes swaps effortless. Whether you're unboxing materials, trimming tape, or cutting plastics, this knife delivers clean, accurate cuts with minimal effort. The durable ABS plastic body features a multi-position slide lock that allows you to quickly set and secure your cutting depth, while the smooth blade slider ensures easy operation and blade stability during use. The extended blade guide offers added control and helps prevent blade breakage. Includes a built-in tether hole for attaching a lanyard or wall storage. Compatible with all standard 18mm snap-off blades, the OX Trade Snap Off Utility knife is dependable for general-purpose cutting. Cut safer, faster and smarter with OX.
column55: The OX Trade 18mm Snap-Off Utility Knife is a compact retractable boxcutter built for everyday cutting tasks. column5: Forged Steel Head: Durable steel construction ensures exceptional strength and performance for tough job site conditions and heavy-duty construction applications., Milled Striking Face for Precision: The textured face enhances grip on nail heads, reducing the risk of slips and ensuring precise and consistent strikes., Steel-Reinforced Hickory Handle: The genuine American hickory handle is reinforced with a steel shaft for added strength, minimizing vibration and resisting wear and cracking., Curved Handle Design: Ergonomically designed curved handle offers better leverage, control, and shock absorption, reducing user fatigue during prolonged use., TPR Rubber Grip: The contoured, non-slip TPR grip provides superior comfort and control, ensuring a secure hold even in challenging jobsite conditions., Magnetic Nail Starter: Simplifies one-handed nail placement, boosting accuracy and efficiency, especially in framing, decking, and roofing tasks., Versatile Application: Suitable for framing, carpentry, demolition, and woodworking, making it an essential tool for professionals and serious DIYers alike.
column54:
The OX Tools Pro 22-Ounce Curved Hickory Handle Framing Hammer is expertly designed for professional tradesmen and DIY enthusiasts, offering durability, comfort, and precision for demanding construction and woodworking tasks. Built with a forged steel head, milled face, and a steel-reinforced hickory handle, this hammer combines strength and advanced features to tackle rigorous jobsite conditions.

At the heart of this hammer’s performance is the forged steel head with a milled face, ensuring precise strikes and a secure grip on nail heads to reduce slips and glancing blows. Its straight claw design allows for efficient nail removal and versatility in a variety of framing, carpentry, and demolition tasks.

The curved hickory handle, crafted from genuine American hickory wood, delivers excellent shock absorption, reducing vibration with every strike. Reinforced with a steel shaft that extends into the head, this handle offers additional strength, ensuring resistance to cracking and wear even under heavy use. The ergonomic curve enhances leverage and control, making every swing more effective.

For comfort during extended use, the handle features a TPR rubber grip, ergonomically contoured to fit snugly in your hand. This grip provides superior comfort and slip resistance, ensuring secure handling in wet or dry conditions, which is essential for all-day use. A standout feature is the magnetic nail starter, designed to simplify one-handed nail placement.
column55: The OX Tools Pro 22-Ounce Framing Hammer combines professional-grade durability with user-focused design. Featuring a forged steel head, milled face, and a steel-reinforced hickory handle, it delivers ultimate striking power. Its TPR rubber grip enhances comfort, while a magnetic nail starter streamlines tasks. Built for demanding construction and woodworking projects.

column54:
The OX Trade Auto-Retract Utility Knife is a self-retracting box cutter designed to enhance safety. The auto-retracting blade mechanism automatically retracts the blade into the body when the thumb button is released - helping reduce the risk of on-site injuries. 

Constructed with a durable metal body, this utility knife is made to last through constant use on the job. It includes 5 premium SK5 blackened utility blades, each double-sided for long-lasting performance and extended value. When it’s time to swap blades, the tool-free thumb screw allows for fast and easy changes. No tools required to change the blade, no downtime.

The internal storage compartment holds up to five spare box cutter blades, so you're always prepared. The tether hole offers attachment to a lanyard or hook storage.

Whether you're opening boxes, trimming plastic, or slicing through materials on site, the OX Trade Auto-Retract Utility Knife combines professional-grade construction with enhanced safety features.

The auto-retracting blade mechanism automatically retracts the blade into the body when the thumb button is released, helping reduce the risk of on-site injuries.

column54: Built with the tradesman in mind, the OX Ultrastrike Framing Hammer is comfortable yet powerful. The OX Ultrastrike Framing Hammers are constructed from one-piece of forged steel which is built to withstand any jobsite condition. The magnetic nail starter on the head allows for simple handling and overall use as it is easier for you to line up your nail precisely. The bridged neck of the hammer is designed to absorb strike shock and vibration which reduces user strain. Limiting the vibration of the hammer helps to reduce repetitive stress injuries and pains. Built tough and durable, the hammer is also designed to be comfortable and ergonomic for day-to-day use. The nonslip OX Grip is made to help users hold the hammer with ease while remaining comfortable throughout the working day. The hammer is heat treated to give it greater overall durability as well as allow it to last longer over time.
column55: OX Tools Ultrastrike Framing Hammers are created with the tradesmen in mind. This Ultrastrike Framing Hammer was designed by professionals, for professionals. Our non-slip OX Grip handle and bridged neck for shock reduction help you to live the trade. Forged, one piece steel construction ensures the durability of the tool while the magnetic nail starter allows for easier handling and use.

column55:
Built with the tradesman in mind, the OX Pro Series Tuff Levels are designed to take a beating. The aluminum
body of the level is one solid piece, without handles or room for cement, mud, and other debris to get clogged.
The level includes three vials, one for level, two for plumb. The vials consistently provide an accuracy of 0. 005"/
1" or . 5mm/ m and are protected by structural reinforcement within the level. On each end of the body there
are rubber end caps to protect the level from bumps, drops, and excess damage. The top and bottom of the level
are both milled surfaces giving it a perfectly at edge and ensuring increased accuracy compared to a coated
surface.
